<refsection condition="ref.description">
<title>Description</title><para>The <tag>author</tag> element holds information about the
      author of a document. When inside one of the bibliographic elements,
      <tag>author</tag> refers to the author of the document described
      by that element. Otherwise, it refers to the author of the current
      document or document section.</para>

      <refsection><info><title>Processing expectations</title></info>
        

        <para>May be formatted inline or as a displayed block, depending on
